ComicInfo.Title: The Scourge of the Super-Skrull!; We, Who Are About to Die...!
ComicInfo.Summary:
The Scourge of the Super-Skrull!: The Super-Skrull, influenced by Loki, attacks and is beaten by Thor. Meanwhile, Odin sends Sif and Balder to find the evil Enchanters in the land of Ringsfjord.
We, Who Are About to Die...!: Mogul's Demon Riders attack Thor and his companions.
